==文化意义==
在暖温带、中温带和高原温带地区的[[寺庙|寺庙]]中常种植[[垂柳|垂柳]]和旱柳，作为[[中国无忧花|中国无忧花]]的替代树种，以表达[[佛教|佛教]]的[[无忧|无忧]]之意<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Wang |first1=Xinyang |last2=Jin |first2=Cheng |last3=Huang |first3=Li |last4=Zhou |first4=Lihua |last5=Zheng |first5=Mingming |last6=Qian |first6=Shenhua |last7=Yang |first7=Yongchuan |title=Plant diversity and species replacement in Chinese Buddhist temples |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2020-06-20 |volume=28 |issue=6 |pages=668 |doi=10.17520/biods.2019392}}</ref>。


